    "These early developments set the stage for the Transformer model, which has shown remarkable proficiency in tasks like text classification and sentiment analysis.In 2015, Elon Musk and others endowed one billion dollars for the establishment of Open AI as a nonprofit organization to prepare against the unintended action of robotics and AI [16].",
